system.controller

Class OverLayerController

  • java.lang.Object
    • system.model.LVSObject
      • system.controller.OverLayerController

  • public class OverLayerController
extends LVSObject
    This class is the controller of the over layer which used to display additional HCI support for VTKPanel. This layer exist due to no only the compatibility problem of VTK and MacOS, but also the API used for draw java UI and VTKPanel. Since AWT was a heavy-weight component, and its drawing sequence was after Swing. Such that, it is not implementable to draw this layer in the origin JFrame. If OpenGL Canvas is used for the implementation this layer could be reduced.
    Version:
    1.2
    Author:
    Andy Tsang
